Contains the bussiness logic used for the Matador game.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Die
    Provides a pseudo random die.
    Game
    Controller for the game that is responsible for running the game using the other classes in the project.
    Konto
    Konto used to represent the balance of the Player.
    MatadorRafleBaeger
    Provides a MatadorRafleBaeger containing either two or a custom number of pseudo random six-sided dice.
    Player
    Provides a Player that is used in a dice game.
    TestMatadorRafleBaeger
    Tests MatadorRafleBaeger to see if it is random.
